pinenote-gnome-extension (1.8-dev) UNRELEASED; urgency=medium

  * Suppress confirmation dialog by blocking the corresponding signal - change
    contributed by user hrdl. Thanks for that!
  * The state of the various settings should now persist between reboots. Old
	settings are applied to the system using the dbus service. Thanks Peter
    Nerlich for this huge patch set!
  * Much better usage of dbus routines to set ebc module parameters
  * Gnome 48 support

 -- Maximilian Weigand <mweigand@mweigand.net>  Fri, 04 Apr 2025 18:38:59 +0200

